The textures of Sun and Earth are released under CC BY 4.0 (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/)
Please refer to this website for more informations: https://www.solarsystemscope.com/textures/

Quoted from the website:
 "Textures in this pack are based on NASA elevation and imagery data.
  Colors and shades of the textures are tuned accordng to true-color
  photos made by Messenger, Viking and Cassini spacecrafts, and, of
  course, the Hubble Space Telescope."